Mission accomplished!

55
00:09:54,972 --> 00:09:55,894
That's a keeper!

56
00:09:57,436 --> 00:10:00,599
It's alright, tough guy.
You got them all.

57
00:10:04,904 --> 00:10:07,747
Don't worry, Bolt.
You've saved the day again.

58
00:10:24,076 --> 00:10:24,819
<i>Good boy!</i>

59
00:10:25,811 --> 00:10:26,502
<i>Airport!</i>

60
00:10:35,263 --> 00:10:37,356
<i>Bolt, speak!</i>

61
00:10:40,512 --> 00:10:43,337
- Boom mike!
- It's a boom mike.

62
00:10:45,582 --> 00:10:47,079
That's sloppy!

63
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:49,114
The dog could have seen it.

64
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:51,289
He could have seen that.

65
00:10:51,311 --> 00:10:54,562
Uh, who cares
if the dog sees a boom mike?

66
00:10:56,550 --> 00:11:00,387
Forgive me for answering a question with a question!

67
00:11:00,895 --> 00:11:03,804
But, who are you?

68
00:11:04,271 --> 00:11:06,441
Mindy Parker,
from the network.

69
00:11:07,046 --> 00:11:11,189
Of course... Let me ask you,
Mindy from the network.

70
00:11:12,077 --> 00:11:13,784
What do you see here?

71
00:11:15,848 --> 00:11:18,816
- The dog?
- The dog, she says.

72
00:11:19,518 --> 00:11:24,220
O, Mindy... poor, poor Mindy!

73
00:11:24,423 --> 00:11:26,811
Am I... missing something?

74
00:11:26,947 --> 00:11:29,324
You're missing everything, Mindy.

75
00:11:29,616 --> 00:11:33,161
You see a dog...
I see an animal,

76
00:11:33,161 --> 00:11:37,503
who believes with every fiber of his being...
every fiber...

77
00:11:37,993 --> 00:11:40,587
That the girl he loves
is in mortal danger.

78
00:11:40,608 --> 00:11:42,791
I see a depth of emotion on the face of that canine,

79
00:11:42,792 --> 00:11:47,194
the likes of which has never been captured on screen before.

80
00:11:47,104 --> 00:11:49,535
Never, Mindy from the network.

81
00:11:51,235 --> 00:11:55,787
We jump through hoops to make sure that Bolt believes everything is real.

82
00:11:56,350 --> 00:11:59,259
It's why we don't miss marks.
It's why we don't reshoot.

83
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:01,420
And it's we why most certainly,

84
00:12:01,421 --> 00:12:04,497
do not let the dog see boom mikes.

85
00:12:06,965 --> 00:12:10,032
Because, Mindy from the network...

86
00:12:11,195 --> 00:12:14,111
if the dog believes it

87
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:18,422
the audience believes it.

88
00:12:20,111 --> 00:12:24,818
Wow, okay, you want reality?
Here you go chief.

89
00:12:24,931 --> 00:12:26,557
The show's too predictable

90
00:12:26,584 --> 00:12:29,489
The girl's in danger, the dog saves her from the creepy English guy.

91
00:12:29,490 --> 00:12:31,353
We get it, there's always a happy ending.

92
00:12:31,426 --> 00:12:34,862
And, our focus groups tell us,
that 18 to 35 year-olds are unhappy.

93
00:12:34,875 --> 00:12:36,575
They're not happy with happy.

94
00:12:36,536 --> 00:12:38,874
So, maybe you should, I don't know,

95
00:12:38,875 --> 00:12:41,344
spend a little less time worrying about the dog's method acting,

96
00:12:41,597 --> 00:12:42,617
and more time into

97
00:12:42,618 --> 00:12:44,221
figuring out how to stop
20 year-olds in Topeka

98
00:12:44,222 --> 00:12:45,332
from changing the channel.

99
00:12:45,367 --> 00:12:49,157
Because if you lose so much as
half a ratings point, so help me,

100
00:12:49,158 --> 00:12:52,537
I will fire everyone in this room,
starting with you.

101
00:12:53,516 --> 00:12:54,529
How's that for real?

102
00:12:58,326 --> 00:13:00,490
There... perfect.

103
00:13:02,775 --> 00:13:04,226
You saved me again, Bolt.

104
00:13:06,282 --> 00:13:07,981
It's okay,
it's nothing.

105
00:13:09,068 --> 00:13:10,184
No more bad guys.

106
00:13:12,294 --> 00:13:13,996
Ah? Are you hungry?

107
00:13:19,479 --> 00:13:20,658
You got it, Bolt.

108
00:13:20,659 --> 00:13:21,974
No one's going to hurt me.

109
00:13:24,147 --> 00:13:25,358
Bolt look at me!

110
00:13:25,158 --> 00:13:26,662
I'm fine, see?

111
00:13:29,215 --> 00:13:30,738
Come here buddy! Come here!

112
00:13:33,015 --> 00:13:34,844
Go get it Bolt!
Go get it!

113
