115
00:13:44,998 --> 00:13:46,521
Mr. Carrot.

116
00:14:05,382 --> 00:14:06,568
Oh, Bolt!

117
00:14:08,260 --> 00:14:09,924
You know I have to go.

118
00:14:25,032 --> 00:14:26,865
Yeah, you're my good boy.

119
00:14:34,943 --> 00:14:38,142
And there she is, my little superstar.

120
00:14:38,143 --> 00:14:40,038
Let's get to that Teen Vogue cover shoot.

121
00:14:40,442 --> 00:14:43,570
Mom, I want to take Bolt home this weekend.

122
00:14:43,644 --> 00:14:47,623
- Well, I, um...
- Ah, that would be nice, that would be great...

123
00:14:48,085 --> 00:14:49,978
A little girl and her dog.

124
00:14:51,022 --> 00:14:52,129
Nothing better than that.

125
00:14:54,359 --> 00:14:57,234
