139
00:15:37,263 --> 00:15:39,146
I will do anything for her.

140
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:44,246
And I would trade her for you in a heartbeat.
...True story.

141
00:15:44,894 --> 00:15:47,547
That reminds me, we need to be getting over to wardrobe,

