144
00:16:03,782 --> 00:16:07,577
Oh yeah, you're new. Guy never leaves the set.

145
00:16:07,578 --> 00:16:11,695
It's unbelievable. Whenever I get a chance,
it's the perfect way to unwind.

146
00:16:14,273 --> 00:16:15,830
I like to start with an evil laugh.

147
00:16:20,182 --> 00:16:22,224
Hello, hairballs!

148
00:16:22,667 --> 00:16:26,551
You may have won today Bolt,
But, in the end...

149
00:16:26,931 --> 00:16:29,782
We will get your little Penny.

150
00:16:29,825 --> 00:16:33,303
Not likely, cat.
For you have chosen to follow the path of evil,

151
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:37,377
