for you to take back to your green-eyed man.

159
00:17:06,074 --> 00:17:08,338
You tell him,
that his old friend, Bolt...

160
00:17:08,339 --> 00:17:09,455
Is it long?

161
00:17:10,308 --> 00:17:12,652
Is what long?
- The message!

162
00:17:12,714 --> 00:17:16,586
Is it a long message?
Because I have a horrible memory.

163
00:17:16,587 --> 00:17:19,170
I'll make it brief, all right?
You tell him, that I said that I'm gonna...

164
00:17:19,171 --> 00:17:20,299
You know what? Why don't we do this?

165
00:17:20,925 --> 00:17:24,989
You remember the first half of the message,
and then I remember the second,

166
00:17:24,991 --> 00:17:27,354
then we can pass it on to the green-eyed man together.

167
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:29,731
I don't care how the message is translated.

168
00:17:29,732 --> 00:17:31,841
