203
00:20:23,845 --> 00:20:29,083
I'm sure, he'll be more accommodating,
now that I've got

204
00:20:29,084 --> 00:20:31,108
his lucky Penny.

205
00:20:31,578 --> 00:20:32,348
Bolt!

206
00:20:34,569 --> 00:20:38,113
World domination is within my grasp.

207
00:20:49,843 --> 00:20:52,493
