Bolt, it's okay.
I'm fine!

211
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:06,575
Whoa, whoa, guards stop her!

212
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:08,911
- Hey, Hey!
- Hold on!

213
00:21:09,170 --> 00:21:14,098
- Listen to him. He needs to know that I'm okay.
- Nope, you're not okay.

214
00:21:14,102 --> 00:21:17,200
