Dr. Calico.

215
00:21:17,201 --> 00:21:19,501
At least, that's what the dog needs to think.

216
00:21:19,502 --> 00:21:23,053
Just imagine, close your eyes and
just imagine how excited he will be

217
00:21:23,055 --> 00:21:26,323
